sealed.name: Outlaws of Thunder Junction Play Booster Pack

extendedData.name: OracleText
extendedData.value:
In Outlaws of Thunder Junction, your players will join Oko's crew of deadly desperados as they plot a heist in the frontier world of Thunder Junction. They'll face harsh deserts, hostile critters, and even rival outlaws—but with grit and gumption, they'll ride off into the sunset.
The Bundle is a great gift for Magic superfans visiting your store. They contain a little bit of everything to get a player's collection off the ground, plus an oversized Spindown life counter themed after the set.
Contents:
• 9 Outlaws of Thunder Junction Play Boosters
• Each Play Booster includes a combination of 1–5 cards of rarity Rare or higher and 3–6 Uncommon, 5–8 Common, and 1 Land cards. 1 card of any rarity is Traditional Foil. Foil Borderless Mythic Planeswalker in <1% of boosters. Traditional Foil Land replaces a Land in 20% of boosters. List card included in 20% of Play Boosters.
• 1 Traditional Foil card with Bundle-exclusive alternate-art
• 15 Traditional Foil Basic Land cards (5 with Full Art)
• 15 nonfoil Basic Land cards (5 with Full Art)
• 1 oversized Spindown life counter
• 1 card storage box
• 2 reference cards
